# Tutorial video debug artifacts (written only under --debug). Never commit:
# split-pane scene IDs contain ':' which is an illegal path char on Windows and
# breaks `git checkout` (exit 128) on windows-latest CI runners.
*.debug-frames/

# Tutorial/solution media synced to Cloudflare R2 (media.rediacc.com).
# Not committed -- see .ci/docs/r2-media-setup.md. Restore via
# .ci/scripts/deploy/sync-media-from-r2.sh or ./run.sh www tutorials generate.
# NOTE: these entries only take effect once the directories are removed from
# git tracking (git rm) -- adding a path to .gitignore does not untrack
# already-committed files. See root CLAUDE.md's "Media Assets" section.
public/assets/tutorials/video/
public/assets/videos/solutions/
public/assets/tutorials/audio/
